{"data":[{"id":562660757,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f476b16d98a7eda02c83663a0baa9db6","url_token":"wang-zhao-feng-60-19","name":"王兆丰","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/d76fff42d40f81af3887a2164ed17585_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/d76fff42d40f81af3887a2164ed17585_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f476b16d98a7eda02c83663a0baa9db6","user_type":"people","headline":"一个忧郁的乌龟","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":40,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562660757","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546132084,"updated_time":1546132084,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"先回答问题～\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e能，当然能上清北！\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e哥猜肯定不是个简单的问题。虽然我也不是很懂，但是从概率上来说，巅峰欧拉都无法证明，陈景润等人用了半生才半证明，我不相信你能证明。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e因为据我所知，在我们行业，这种级别的问题，你要自创一套体系才行。而且很大程度上你的这个体系不是突然提出的，前人或多或少都有提及和发展才能到解决哥猜的程度。而目前关于哥猜这个证明的研究进展，前面搞数学的大V已经回答或提到了，甚至贴出了相关论文，我看了一下其中的内容，个人觉得那绝对不是高中数学或高中自学能达到的水平。这个水平你肯定达不到，不是你智商或资质不够，而是需要时间才能消化吸收，你一出生就开始研究都不够。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e高考的压力的确很大，我当时也能感受到。如果你的问题是＂数学很好怎么保送清北？＂，相信知乎上很多人都会给你中肯的回答，甚至一些过来人能给你宝贵的建议。我的建议是修改问题，好好复习，争取一下，而不是说元旦发布证明过程这种上头的话。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e年轻的时候不能看轻自己，更不能过于看重自己。尤其是不自觉地消费自己，特别是在这个大网络时代。知乎上很多吃瓜群众都在消费你，这个问题成为一个大型审丑的事件。你一定不能陷进去，还是要脚踏实地点，即便你是个数学天才，因为天才特别容易陨落。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e如果说关于怎么保送清北的话，其实没必要这么麻烦，你只要发表1篇国内数学顶刊的文章，应该就有人会给你写清北自主招生的推荐信了，大概率会被清北录取，因为你已经一定程度证明了自己的学术能力。当然这只是我个人看法，请各位清北的大牛指正。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e再如果你只是想涨粉，那就好好运作吧，这世界实现自身价值的方法不止上清北一种，至少目前我看你很有炒作的天赋～\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e祝你顺利！","editable_content":"","excerpt":"先回答问题～ 能，当然能上清北！ 哥猜肯定不是个简单的问题。虽然我也不是很懂，但是从概率上来说，巅峰欧拉都无法证明，陈景润等人用了半生才半证明，我不相信你能证明。 因为据我所知，在我们行业，这种级别的问题，你要自创一套体系才行。而且很大程度…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1048\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2